  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/284050/extras/fc27b5336562acc87d228245feedafa9.poster.avif?t=1753576725\" width=600 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/284050/extras/fc27b5336562acc87d228245feedafa9.webm?t=1753576725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/284050/extras/fc27b5336562acc87d228245feedafa9.mp4?t=1753576725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/284050/extras/dd5cdf82b7f612065f8c37217176dd33.webp?t=1753576725\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br>After a car accident, you wake up in a gloomy asylum with your head wrapped in bandages. Many questions remain, but the most important one to solve is: what are you doing here? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/284050/extras/0d6be069ad87e1eda6366c747d0cbbaa.poster.avif?t=1753576725\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/284050/extras/0d6be069ad87e1eda6366c747d0cbbaa.webm?t=1753576725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/284050/extras/0d6be069ad87e1eda6366c747d0cbbaa.mp4?t=1753576725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/284050/extras/8ba21dba78ab4450936fc67aa35de48e.webp?t=1753576725\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br>Sanitarium features a plot intricate set in an intense dark world where a very thin line separates senses from madness. There are many riddles to solve throughout this immersive and captivating adventure that will make your head spin with terror. <br><br>Even now, Sanitarium is a masterwork suitable for point-and-click beginners, confirmed or riddle-solving experts who enjoy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/284050/extras/c125da04900c4d14df1d8df22c686f0c.poster.avif?t=1753576725\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/284050/extras/c125da04900c4d14df1d8df22c686f0c.webm?t=1753576725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/284050/extras/c125da04900c4d14df1d8df22c686f0c.mp4?t=1753576725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
